<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" xmlns:html="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idf6866eac-2930-11f1-96a8-b9bd2a0a99b5" identifier="/us/usc/t46/s8903"><num value="8903">§ 8903.</num><heading> Self-propelled, uninspected passenger vessels</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">A self-propelled, uninspected passenger vessel shall be operated by an individual licensed by the Secretary to operate that type of vessel, under prescribed regulations.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idf6866ead-2930-11f1-96a8-b9bd2a0a99b5">(<ref href="/us/pl/98/89">Pub. L. 98–89</ref>, <date date="1983-08-26">Aug. 26, 1983</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/97/555">97 Stat. 555</ref>; <ref href="/us/pl/99/307/s1/14/B">Pub. L. 99–307, § 1(14)(B)</ref>, (C), <date date="1986-05-19">May 19, 1986</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/100/446">100 Stat. 446</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
